name: Blade Of Chaos
description: The Blades of Chaos were forged in the darkest depths of the Underworld by the God of War (Ares). This sword is equipped with a chain that is able to expand the range of attacks once the user uses it in battle. the user's faithfulness in offering his service to the god of war Ares. They are filled with fire, which allows them to ignite with every attack the user makes supporting waves of brutal attacks regardless of the people around them.
